{"tid":1363230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［遍地開花］康文署員工想講人話","createTime":"2019-07-25T06:12:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T09:04:02.000Z","uid":49833,"like":56,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"dd983a320b488d6be53e99c5e37c01ab2c8aaef7","tid":1363230,"uid":49833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:12:02.000Z","msg":"各位香港市民：<br />\n<br />\n自政府強推逃犯條例修訂以來，社會紛爭不斷。無論市民以何種方式表達對反修例的意見，政府依舊視若無睹。<br />\n<br />\n除了政府漠視民意，警察的言行同樣令人髮指。先有拒絕出示委任證，對示威者甚至記者使用不必要武力；再有縱容黑社會暴力，令無辜市民受傷及引起公眾恐慌。我們對警隊徹底失去信心，不能置信這竟然發生於香港。同為政府員工，我們實在恥與為伍。<br />\n<br />\n最後，我們要求問責官員出來承擔責任，政府正面回應五大訴求，包括：撤回逃犯修例、確保抗爭者公平審訊、撤回暴動定性、成立獨立調查委員會及實行基本法承諾的真普選。<br />\n<br />\n康文署職員上<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ctm9Arf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fctm9Arf.png&h=fea136a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（代po）"},{"pid":"f77e7d518d0d7ae178ad6517a94be1f11196e31f","tid":1363230,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:12:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3330da3b72eef5d6523a10e7325d2fd756e318aa","tid":1363230,"uid":218309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:13:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e87a076a2ba965c0f93f975bb4acbf5586241aad","tid":1363230,"uid":99856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:13:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2703a7249b4b4400d34322bc27fd595ec4889fe","tid":1363230,"uid":49833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:13:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n726 機場<br />\n727 元朗<br />\n728 中上環<br />\n<br />\n同我推爆佢</span></span>"},{"pid":"be073ff2da9cdfcc51fd91d4df279ae12e5be91f","tid":1363230,"uid":210912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:13:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"03174a6e4259b3cba26d74ca49f86aa0ff7f3a4c","tid":1363230,"uid":4